race.comment: DRAGON TALES (2) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this calibre. Tuned up for this with a recent trial placing and a strong showing while fresh would not surprise. OLD GOLD (4) just ran into one better at Rockhampton before being tipped out for further time to furnish. Set for a bold return. GOT THIS (11) has placed four of six overall and only needs some luck navigating from the sticky alley to be playing a role in the outcome. HAPHAZARD (3) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown ability at the trials and won't need to be a superstar to be competitive against this lot. Respect any market confidence. MISTER DOOBEE (6) next in line from the inside marble.
